994498344,ALPR-for-Peruvian-License-Plates,joelibaceta/ALPR-for-Peruvian-License-Plates,,,Jupyter Notebook,"Jupyter Notebook, Python, TeX",1,0,1,0,2025-06-02T03:09:51Z,2025-09-15T09:55:13Z,2025-06-06T01:18:48Z,,"# ALPR for Peruvian License Plates 🇵🇪 This repository contains a working application for **Automatic License Plate Recognition (ALPR)** tailored to Peruvian road conditions. The pipeline detects vehicles, locates license plates within them, and extracts their alphanumeric content using OCR. --- ## 🎯 What This Project Does - Detects vehicles in road video footage - Locates license plates (painted or metallic) using a custom YOLOv7-based model - Applies OCR to extract and validate plate numbers <p align=""center""> <img src=""figs/dataset_vehicle_sample.png"" width=""600""/> </p>"
