356348116,flutter_fvm,goandreus/flutter_fvm,Flutter Version Management,,Dart,"Dart, Swift, Kotlin, Objective-C",1,0,1,0,2021-04-09T17:19:52Z,2023-03-14T21:32:31Z,2021-04-09T23:20:47Z,,"# fvmtest Configuracion inicial FVM ## Instalar Dart ``` brew tap dart-lang/dart brew install dart ``` ## Iniciamos FVM ``` pub global activate fvm ``` ## Instalamos versiones del SDK ``` fvm install <version> fvm install 1.22.6 (Ultimo soporte, la mayoria de proyectos la utiliza) fvm install 2.0.0 (No-null safety, aqui ya la mayoria de Widgets son deprecados) fvm install 2.0.3 (actual - null safety) ``` ## Ver nuestra lista de versiones ``` fvm list ``` ## Elegimos la version que deseemos usar ``` fvm use <version> fvm use 1.22.6 fvm use 2.0.0 ``` ## Configuracion para VS CODE ``` En el apartado de ""view"" seleccionar ""command palette"" escribir y seleccionar ""Open Setting(JSON)"" Agregamos ""dart.flutterSdkPaths"": ["".fvm/flutter_sdk""] ```"
